textable
========

Generate *tex* and *pdf* files from dataframes.

Installation
------------

::

   pip install textable

Minimal Example
---------------

The following script (content of ``examples/minimal.py``) will generate
``build/table.tex`` and ``build/table.pdf``, an existing ``build``
directory is necessary.

.. code:: python

   import numpy as np
   import pandas as pd
   from textable import TexTable

   df = pd.DataFrame(np.ones((3, 3)), columns=['A', 'B', 'C'])
   table = TexTable(df, "build/table")
   table.generate_pdf()


